{{Expand Dutch|Bram van der Lek|date=December 2013}}
[[File:Tweede Kamer debat over buitenlandse werknemers, Van de Lek (PSP) - NL-HaNA 2.24.01.05 0 927-5180 WM247.jpg|thumb|200px|Bram van der Lek in October 1974.]]
'''Bram van der Lek''' (20 May 1931 <U+2013> 29 November 2013) was a [[Dutch people|Dutch]] politician and author. Representing the [[Pacifist Socialist Party]], he was a member of the [[House of Representatives (Netherlands)|House of Representatives]] from 1967 until 1971 and from 1972 until 1978, the [[Senate (Netherlands)|Senate]] from 1983 until 1984, and the [[European Parliament]] from 1984 until 1989. He also wrote a book in 1972,  ''Het Milieuboekje (The Environment Booklet)'', which was about environmental issues of the time.<ref>[http://www.nrc.nl/nieuws/2013/11/30/psp-voorman-bram-van-der-lek-82-overleden/ PSP-voorman Bram van der Lek (82) overleden] {{nl icon}}</ref>

